
            Video
            Ballon d'Or: Presenter's awkward moment with first ever female winner
            Lyon and Norway forward Ada Hegerberg had just won football's most prestigious award when the host, DJ Martin Solveig, asked her to twerk.It was the first time a female player was presented with the award - voted for by journalists - which recognises the best players in the world.Real Madrid's Luca Modric won the men's category, and Pars Saint-Germain's Kylian Mbappe won the youth prize.
                
                        04 Dec 2018
                    
                
        
